room_title: Escape room "Defused" by Locked Up - Mishawaka in South Bend
room_description:
A theft has been reported at a local U.S. Army base, and two chemical bombs are missing. As agents in the Department of Homeland Security, you have received a tip from a familiar source known only as “The Chemist”.
Extensive research and valuable intel has led you to “The Chemist’s” laboratory. Upon entry, the door is sealed behind you and the entire room is wired to blow. Will you be able to escape?
